data.meta_description:
The Digital Archive provides access to the history of Philander Smith University. The site features selections from the unique archival holdings of the D.W. Reynolds Library Archives and Special Collections Unit.

Philander Smith University History- Browse the Exhibits section to view pages related to the history of PSC, Faculty, and Alumni.

Items in Archive- Browse the Digital Collections section to view PSU material culture items housed in the Archives.

Send questions or comments to kanderson@philander.edu
